---
// src/pages/privacy-policy.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Dazzle handles inquiry and consultation information shared through this website.">
  <section class="container p-4 mt-4 mb-4 privacy-page">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Dazzle handles information you share when you browse the website, submit a product inquiry, or request a consultation.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as your name, phone number, email address, selected product, consultation preference, and message details.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to product inquiries and consultation requests.</li>
      <li>Discuss product availability, pricing, customization, delivery, and care questions.</li>
      <li>Improve our website, product information, and customer support process.</li>
      <li>Maintain basic inquiry records and meet applicable legal requirements.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share limited information with trusted service providers that help operate the website, process form submissions, communicate with you, or support customer service.</p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect submitted information. However, no internet transmission or storage system can be guaranteed as completely secure.</p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <p>You may ask us to access, correct, or delete inquiry information you previously shared, subject to practical and legal retention requirements.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy when website features, business processes, or legal requirements change. The latest version will be posted on this page.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>

    <p class="text-small mt-4"><em>Last updated: May 28, 2026</em></p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .text-small {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #777;
  }

  .container h2 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .container ul {
    margin-left: 2rem;
    list-style: disc;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .container li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
